  "texts": [
    "The above mechanism can well adapt to brightness changes and effectively capture the target.",
    "The distinction between the background and the background in order to extract crucial information more effectively.",
    "This attention mechanism calculates weights expressing the relevance of pixels using an energy function, as indicated in Eq.",
    "where, t = w t + b t and xi = w t x i + b t are linear transformations of t and x i, t and x i are the target and input features, respectively.w t and b t represent weights and biases, respectively.",
